{"tid":1505164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成個運動，個個得把口，覺得出去行完就會贏咁，返到屋企都可以抗爭架","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T14:23:41.000Z","uid":120377,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"aad9bb3d924e1cde25b4dcf82e538fbe69b9e231","tid":1505164,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:03:28.000Z","msg":"成日講到黑警做d野幾大獲，用黎做文宣最好，拎住幾多核彈，睇到個人好嬲好嬲。<br />\n問心呀，講完睇完，仲有無做其他野？<br />\n放上twitter reddit有無做？成班得把口，下面係隔離post拎既，你地有無同外國講？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U56J7Rf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU56J7Rf.png&h=9e21cc08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別係文宣組，做極都係集會既圖，演唱會poster都係做一張就夠啦屌，比盡你咪做多張詳細版，十幾張都係講一個event，要睇要去，一早知道哂。<br />\n<br />\n求下你地做多d黑警同政府所作所為既圖出黎啦。<br />\n外國無人知架，香港個市場飽和啦，用多d資源做出國際啦。<br />\nChinazi有無人做呀？警黑勾結呢？曱甴去人化呢？<br />\n就算做左圖，都無人放上網比外國知，個個就出post話有新核彈算。<br />\n<br />\n下面係我同朋友整既，未必表達哂所有野，因為唔夠人同時間做，而我都想搵designer同英文手足幫手做野。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我地都要人幫手publish出去比外國<br />\n<br />\n我求下你地唔好淨係睇新聞同圍爐，人地用真槍啦屌，要屠殺我地啦。玩膠開心完，做認真野啦好唔好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTLnD1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTLnD1T.jpg&h=5e138276&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhdHD1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhdHD1T.jpg&h=7b20fd1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u95VY1U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu95VY1U.jpg&h=c6925cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85SxgOz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85SxgOz.jpg&h=d7e3d5ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BTDTLGV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBTDTLGV.jpg&h=6a648beb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfnAY1W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfnAY1W.jpg&h=3582b4dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"327ba3f6784d65e0fcd6222a5f5074f54a5938a1","tid":1505164,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"屌唔好煩，我去完民陣831就淨係去機場！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505122</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a20e040019ea6464268f7956d5bb7616561c1e2","tid":1505164,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"fc274e4e810d65452ca06b136bff40321dc55450","tid":1505164,"uid":216789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:07:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b85c18047dad5a52a3ec78490928c87c30ea1db8","tid":1505164,"uid":120377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:07:27.000Z","msg":"成班人都得把口話要贏要贏，行完返屋企就訓，成個星期睇記招笑班狗on9，咁就可以贏，個個都搞抗爭啦屌"},{"pid":"9b9bc95bc1e9f8dabd2499c5e381b7be36831d15","tid":1505164,"uid":232295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"我已經po咗上Twitter/Reddit 你又po咗未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b70d264bf17d4f2c92f565fa50708ff0eec7a54","tid":1505164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:08:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e83e6d8a5f1af137b7b15629bf73039e78fd17dc","tid":1505164,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"唔完美，可接受，可改善<br />\nTwitter 見"},{"pid":"70b2121f6fea15948b09748fc19a8ab7885f7d37","tid":1505164,"uid":233534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"次之都話核彈核彈核彈，屌！結果講左成個月，彈何B仔都無力！"},{"pid":"96ef3d405410be90b1d0d5552719cfae40670ea2","tid":1505164,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"